          "en": "He said: Abu al-Qasim Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Qulawayh, may Allah have mercy on him, reported to me from al-Husayn ibn Muhammad ibn Amir, from al-Qasim ibn Muhammad al-Isfahani, from Sulaiman ibn Dawud al-Minqari, from Hammad ibn Isa, from Abu Abdillah Ja'far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon them both, who said:",
